    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 6th level, you can create opening for your allies to exploit, when a creature is affected by a bukijutsu with the combo keyword by you, you may spend a brave order, one allied creature other than you within 30ft of you can target the affected creature with a Bukijutsu Finisher (casted as a finisher) regardless of range, once per turn, using a reaction, ignoring its listed casting time.</p><p>Also at 6th level, you can attack twice, instead of once, whenever you take the Attack action on your turn.</p>",
